# 🔓 Full CTF Decoder v0.0.1

This is a modular Python-based decryption utility for Capture The Flag (CTF) challenges. It performs heuristic and brute-force decoding on unknown text inputs using common encodings and classical ciphers.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔁 Caesar/ROT brute-force (ROT1–ROT25)
- 🔄 ROT13 decoder
- 🔃 Atbash cipher support
- 📡 Morse code decoding
- 🧮 Binary → ASCII
- 🔢 Hexadecimal decoder
- 🧬 Base64 decoder
- 📖 ASCII numeric stream decoder

---

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourname/full-ctf-decoder.git
cd full-ctf-decoder
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt  # (none required yet)
